<div class="noprint plainlinks hlist navbar" style=""><span style="word-spacing:0;">This box:</span>
<ul>
<li class="nv-view"><a href="Template_KarnatakaHistory" title="Template:KarnatakaHistory"><span title="View this template" style="">view</span></a></li>
<li class="nv-talk"><a href="Template_talk_KarnatakaHistory" title="Template talk:KarnatakaHistory"><span title="Discuss this template" style="">talk</span></a></li>
<li class="nv-edit"><a class="external text" href="../../w/index-title=Template_KarnatakaHistory&action=edit.php.html"><span title="Edit this template" style="">edit</span></a></li>
